<h2 id="4发布文章">4.发布文章</h2>
<p>使用命令</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">hugo new posts<span class="se">\f</span>irst-post.md
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>来发布你的第一篇文章吧。</p>
<p>注意文章开头的draft要设置成false才可以渲染文章。</p>
<p><img src="https://i.328888.xyz/2023/02/01/ID885.png" alt="ID885.png"></p>
<h2 id="5-在本地启动你的网站">5. 在本地启动你的网站</h2>
<p>使用以下命令启动网站:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">hugo serve
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>或者</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">hugo server
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>去查看 <code>http://localhost:1313</code>.</p>
<p><img src="https://i.328888.xyz/2023/02/01/8Tiqy.png" alt="8Tiqy.png"></p>
